sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant ChildHost as Child LitElement
    participant ChildRoutes as RoutesController (child)
    participant Outlet as <lit-router-outlet>
    participant ParentRoutes as RoutesController (parent)
    participant Navigation as Navigation controller

    Note over ChildRoutes: Child connects and announces itself
    ChildRoutes->>ChildHost: hostConnected()
    ChildRoutes->>ChildHost: dispatch lit-routes-connected
    ChildHost-->>Outlet: event bubbles
    Outlet->>ParentRoutes: _onRoutesConnected()
    ParentRoutes-->>ChildRoutes: register child + onDisconnect

    Note over Navigation: Navigation discovers parent scope
    Navigation->>ChildHost: dispatch lit-routes-acknowledge
    ChildHost-->>Outlet: event bubbles
    Outlet->>Navigation: set event.current + event.parent
    Navigation-->>Navigation: set current/parent

    Note over ParentRoutes: Tail propagation to children
    ParentRoutes->>ChildRoutes: _propagateNavigation(tailGroup)
